Use to record details of applicants, owners and casework officers

helptext.en:
Applicant

  • The person selected here will replace the Applicant on the Application Details step
  • This field is required

Former Licensee

  • The people selected in this drop down must exist on the Application Details step as a Nominated Excavation Director(s)
  • The people selected here will be removed from the Nominated Excavation Director(s) on the Application Details step
  • This field is required

Nominated Excavation Director

  • The people selected here will be put into the Nominated Excavation Director(s) field on the Application Details step
  • The people provided here must not already exist in the Nominated Excavation Director(s) field on the Application Details step
  • This field is required

Former Employing Body  

  • This field is used to remove an Employing Body from the field on the Application Details page
  • The selected Organisation must exist in the Employing Body field on the on the Application Details page
  • This field is not required

Employing Body

  • This field is used to add an Employing Body to the field on the Application Details page
  • If this field is used without the use of the Former Employing Body field. The selected Employing Body in this field will be added to the Employing Body field on the Application Details page
  • This field is not required

Cur Grade E Decision, Made By (Cur Grade E), Cur Grade D Decision and Made By (Cur Grade D)

  • These fields are not required
  • These fields determine if the transfer will be applied to the field on the Application Details page or closed and not appiled
  • To apply a Transfer of License and see it reflected on the Application Details page. These fields are required and of course must be the positive approval options for the Decision fields
  • One negative approval of the two decision options will mark this as closed. If there was also a Cur Grade D Person and Cur Grade E Person selected
